data.description: This beauty is an Energy Star Home located in the friendly community of Balmoral Park Lakes. It sits on a corner lot, providing a prime location with easy access to the belt-way. As you enter the home, you're greeted by a welcoming foyer and a comfortable layout.  The house include high ceilings, arched entry- walls, granite countertops, and so much more. The large backyard is fully fenced, offering privacy and enough space for outdoor activities.  This home features 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, as well as a formal dining area and a living room. The kitchen has ample storage, pantry, granite countertops, and a breakfast bar for additional seating.  The master bedroom is situated near the back of the home, providing a private and tranquil retreat. It includes a bathroom with a walk-in shower, a garden tub, and a sizable walk-in closet for your convenience.  The property has been immaculately maintained and is ready for you to move in without any additional work needed.
